'''Jraayn''' a faam a [[Vijual aat|vijual aat]] we smadi kiah yuuz difrah-difrah jraayn inschrument fi maak-maak [[Piepa|piepa]] ar wah nex tuu-dimenshanal midiom. Inschrument ingkluud [[Grafait|grafait]] [[Pensl|pensl]], [[Pen ah ingk|pen ah ingk]], [[Ingk|ingk]] [[Brosh|brosh]], wax [[Kola pensl|kola pensl]], [[Krayan|krayan]], [[Chaakuol (aat)|chaakuol]], [[Saidwaak chaak|saidwaak chaak]], [[Pastel|pastel]], difrah-difrah kain a [[Roba|roba]], [[Maaka pen|maaka]], [[Stailos|stailos]], difrah-difrah metal (laka [[Silvapaint|silvapaint]]) ah ilekchanik jraayn.

Di jraayn inschrument riliis wah sumaal amount a matiirial pan a soerfis, lef wah visibl maak. Di muos kaman supuot fi jraayn a [[Piepa|piepa]], alduo adaels matiirial, laka [[Piepabuod|kiaadbuod]], [[Plastik|plastik]], [[Leda|leda]], [[Kianvas|kianvas]], ah [[Lomba|buod]], kiah yuuz. Tempareri jraayn kiah mek pah [[Blakbuod|blakbuod]] ar [[Waitbuod|waitbuod]] ar akchuali liklmuos eniting. Di midiom a eba papila ah fondamental miinz a poblik expreshan rait chuu yuuman ischri. A wan a di simplis ah muos ifishent miinz fi komiunikiet vijual aidie.<ref name=SBTCModule6>[http://www.saylor.org/site/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Module-6.pdf/ Module 6: Media for 2-D Art], Saylor.org, akses 2 April 2012</ref> Di ''h''iizi avielobiliti a jraayn inschrument mek jraayn wan a di muos kaman aatistik aktiviti.

[[File:Munich - Two young women drawing - 5814.jpg|thumb|Smadi a-jraa di [[Baabariini Faan|Baabariini Faan]] ina Miunik]]
In adishan tu di muo aatistik faam, jraayn noftaim yuuz ina komoershal [[Iloschrieshan|iloschrieshan]], [[Chradishanal animieshan|animieshan]], [[Aachitechal jraayn|aachitecha]], [[Injinierin jraayn|injinierin]] ah [[Teknikal jraayn|teknikal jraayn]]. Kuik, friyan jraayn, yuujali no inten az finish wok, sohtaim kaal [[Skech (jraayn)|skech]]. Aatis uu praktis ar wok ina teknikal jraayn kiah kaal [[Jraafta|jraafta]], ar [[Jraafsman|jraafsman]].<ref>http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/draftsman</ref>

